\"n\">using</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Homeomorph.addLeft</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚ÑÇ</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">toPartialHomeomorph.map_nhdsWithin_eq</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Set.mem_univ</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">({</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"bp\">·∂ú</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">|&gt;.</span><span class=\"n\">symm</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The first two lines get it down to the essence of the argument.</p>",
