    {
        "content": "<p>Here is another one that should be easy, but which I found tricky:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">lemma</span> <span class=\"n\">dist_one</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñï</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">dist</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚ÑÇ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üî</span> <span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">refine</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span> <span class=\"n\">H</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Ü¶</span> <span class=\"bp\">?</span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">fun</span> <span class=\"n\">H</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Ü¶</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">H</span><span class=\"o\">]‚ü©</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rwa</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">dist_eq</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">Int.cast_one</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">Int.cast_Nat_cast</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">Int.cast_sub</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">int_cast_abs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">Int.cast_abs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"n\">Int.cast_one</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span> <